The kid covers his ears while looking at me with teary eyes. I check his heartbeats, way too fast, not good.[p]
I give him a shot of Amiodarone from my medical bag and pull him in my arms, trying to calm him down. The woman has stitches on her head but doesn't seem to have any life endangering wound.[p]
I want to wake her up but if she has suicidal tendency like Hoang's father said, maybe it's best to keep her asleep.[p]
I'll wake her up when we're at the hospital. When Hoang gets better, i start dialing the police. [p]
[_tb_end_text]

