#Mr. Phat
I've done everything in my capability!! I come to home early everyday. Give my family everything i had.[p]
Prepare dinner for my son. Do you know how hard it is to get a kid with Cyanotic heart disease to eat? Learn to play piano for my wife because i know she loves music.[p]
Isn't that what a good husband and father has to do???[p]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=1 ]
#Kai
Keep repeating all that nonsense won't make any of them true. Have you ever considered about their feelings?[p]
Do you know how much Hoang is scared at night? Of you?[p]
Do you seriously think your wife wants to be jailed and chloroformed for every "family meeting" or whatever the fuck you called it is?[p]
You and your obsession over that poor woman. You. You and your selfish nature.[p]
All you've ever done is to abuse your power on her and call it "love". That sickening excuse of yours!![p]
[_tb_end_text]

